        "body": "@ledion,  the current implementation will be one TFile per application, while your method will create one TFile per container which would generate more files.\nI guess the reason why the original author adopt TFile is that TFile has one index block which allow user quickly find the value. In this way, user could quickly find one container's log of one application.  ",
